Reasoning: The paper focuses on developing an AI system that forms semantic representations of computer programs, using techniques from knowledge representation and program analysis. This falls under the sub-category of software engineering (cs.SE) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also introduces a new ontology language for modeling computer programs, which falls under programming languages (cs.PL). The use of dataflow graphs and semantic enrichment techniques also suggests a connection to machine learning (cs.LG) and databases (cs.DB).
